00:54:36.050 --> 00:54:40.500
And so the first part of the day
you had to conduct the orchestra.

00:54:40.500 --> 00:54:42.840
Well, I'm so charming.

00:54:42.840 --> 00:54:45.640
I mean I had been, I'm
comfortable on the podium,

00:54:45.640 --> 00:54:47.160
