00:55:13.710 --> 00:55:15.900
But the time I figure out
what key we're in, you know?

00:55:15.900 --> 00:55:19.840
And so, and then the single line
dictation that was like boom, boop,

00:55:19.840 --> 00:55:22.860
boom, boop, stuff, this kind of
stuff, and then the piano record,

00:55:22.860 --> 00:55:24.700
I didn't, my mother couldn't
afford piano lessons.

00:55:24.700 --> 00:55:30.360
